{"tid":1726862,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個話民意唔緊要 平日set路障 假日清路障","createTime":"2019-11-16T09:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T09:34:48.000Z","uid":20028,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3ef4f5a31ed249811b3fa147aab4276043fd1da7","tid":1726862,"uid":20028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:26:55.000Z","msg":"民意係好撚緊要 我地之所以得到咁多人包括國際支持 係因為社會覺得我地做事有原則 就好似開路比救護車 去幫清真寺清潔 每做一次 就愈多人支持我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個禮拜 我地的確有破壞好多野 但係我地要話比人聽我地唔淨係識破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府而加出解放軍清理路障贏掌聲 其實呢件事應該係我地做翻 令人地覺得示威者係有原則同負責任<br />\n<br />\n所以正式宣布 我地要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">平日起路障 假日清路障!!!!!</span>"},{"pid":"fee913b4e325b5bc77faa98820510a12a46d3b9d","tid":1726862,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:27:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5160b0a308fc3486c9a11ff4a158c61fda126a61","tid":1726862,"uid":20028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:29:01.000Z","msg":"推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9c445c50433b495bd490fccf3c75ddd025e7d8","tid":1726862,"uid":20028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:29:27.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"f256cabaf05e639d1a6f03c3d48bf5e7308c4d1b","tid":1726862,"uid":20028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:29:42.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"73152d6b9b0aa4d416c7c8e4472e115a0cef9cc7","tid":1726862,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:29:43.000Z","msg":"都ok, 假日就清囉<br />\n<br />\n轉玩商場戰"},{"pid":"a2e0db65bbe1adf11eafc5f3391e1a5cd9ef425f","tid":1726862,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:30:40.000Z","msg":"對家要比維穩費清架<br />\n咪由佢地比錢囉<br />\n<br />\n我地唔得閒呀, 要出神獸長龍<br />\n勇武又要回氣"},{"pid":"d6816d155501bcb9367c340b9f241a6a64c1ad5c","tid":1726862,"uid":77137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:30:48.000Z","msg":"星期六日清埋去附近位置<br />\n方便平日重用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d466b5577231a48d9239eca484e58f05dfafaaae","tid":1726862,"uid":20028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73152d6b9b0aa4d416c7c8e4472e115a0cef9cc7","tid":1726862,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:29:43.000Z","msg":"都ok, 假日就清囉<br />\n<br />\n轉玩商場戰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:32:00.000Z","msg":"其實而加平日抗爭至係政府個春袋 商場戰會令到市民唔敢出街 反而平日冇得返工 偏偏假期歌舞昇平 最可以得到支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04af3fbca65c79814812a4eb25cc9d385e72fa10","tid":1726862,"uid":222269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:32:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9aa42d84db1f095d7a890d5e386357a4211a83f8","tid":1726862,"uid":335927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:32:23.000Z","msg":"同意，<br />\n例如假日如果可以免費使用隧道，大家會開心好多"},{"pid":"ea9ae6fa9a0aaea180282c82ded7cfb0ec54765a","tid":1726862,"uid":20028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6816d155501bcb9367c340b9f241a6a64c1ad5c","tid":1726862,"uid":77137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:30:48.000Z","msg":"星期六日清埋去附近位置<br />\n方便平日重用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:33:13.000Z","msg":"係 你比人清左下次就冇 你清左放埋一邊冇阻住人反而冇人理 禮拜一又拎翻黎用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128bb8e984c9182bd0493697654695c9da3a6ab6","tid":1726862,"uid":20028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:33:47.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"e52994d04575a1b5bcd4bdc3e49ed082369205f3","tid":1726862,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:34:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72f8d885a308eb0514cec84a259c3479454ff2cc","tid":1726862,"uid":20028,